298
00:23:45,640 --> 00:23:46,799
You go then.

299
00:23:47,160 --> 00:23:48,359
Don't worry. I'll keep watch here.

300
00:23:48,359 --> 00:23:50,160
- I'll call you if there's anything. - Okay.

301
00:23:50,319 --> 00:23:51,359
Go home, take a shower, and get changed.

302
00:23:51,359 --> 00:23:54,079
- Pull yourself together. - Okay, thank you.

303
00:24:03,519 --> 00:24:04,640
Zhou Quan.

304
00:24:06,920 --> 00:24:08,039
Thank you.

305
00:24:24,319 --> 00:24:25,680
Apparently, it was pretty serious.

306
00:24:25,680 --> 00:24:27,079
- Yes. - I heard that too.

307
00:24:27,079 --> 00:24:28,839
