308
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:35,599
Look at this. It's so fun. Did you see this?

309
00:24:35,599 --> 00:24:36,640
My gosh.

310
00:24:41,759 --> 00:24:42,880
Everyone.

311
00:24:44,240 --> 00:24:45,480
