316
00:24:55,720 --> 00:24:57,240
Starting today,

317
00:24:57,440 --> 00:25:00,200
I will be taking over as Zhirong Construction's CEO.

318
00:25:02,119 --> 00:25:03,640
Right now,

319
00:25:04,960 --> 00:25:06,400
the CEO has fallen ill,

320
00:25:06,599 --> 00:25:08,440
the CEO's assistant has been arrested,

321
00:25:08,920 --> 00:25:10,440
