322
00:25:11,240 --> 00:25:13,000
We're in a financial strait.

323
00:25:13,839 --> 00:25:15,519
This is our company's current situation.

324
00:25:16,920 --> 00:25:18,119
I'm still inexperienced,

325
00:25:18,400 --> 00:25:19,880
