326
00:25:19,880 --> 00:25:21,720
after I take over.

327
00:25:22,240 --> 00:25:25,359
So if anyone here wants to leave,

328
00:25:26,000 --> 00:25:28,519
no matter what,

329
00:25:28,519 --> 00:25:31,359
I'll give you severance pay.

330
00:25:32,599 --> 00:25:34,240
If you want to stay,

331
00:25:34,640 --> 00:25:36,119
you have to prepare yourselves.

332
00:25:37,039 --> 00:25:40,279
