336
00:25:53,440 --> 00:25:54,759
I'll wait for you there.

337
00:25:56,640 --> 00:25:57,880
If you want to leave,

338
00:25:58,279 --> 00:25:59,440
go to Zhou Quan...

339
00:25:59,440 --> 00:26:00,960
