00:26:06,799 --> 00:26:08,160
Inform the deputy directors.

341
00:26:13,000 --> 00:26:14,240
This is so sudden.

342
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:15,640
- This is so sudden. - What's going on?

343
00:26:15,640 --> 00:26:17,839
