347
00:28:01,200 --> 00:28:02,319
Have a seat.

348
00:28:12,160 --> 00:28:13,279
Sit down.

349
00:28:14,279 --> 00:28:15,640
Hello, Mr. Hou.

350
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:30,240
I'm sorry. We couldn't retain more people.

351
00:28:30,240 --> 00:28:31,720
