366
00:29:15,079 --> 00:29:16,400
and sitting here today,

367
00:29:16,799 --> 00:29:17,799
I'm very grateful.

368
00:29:17,799 --> 00:29:20,480
I thank you all for your trust and support.

369
00:29:23,119 --> 00:29:24,279
I want to emphasize this.

370
00:29:25,720 --> 00:29:26,880
