371
00:29:29,480 --> 00:29:31,279
Zhirong has gotten to where it is today...

372
00:29:31,279 --> 00:29:32,680
after experiencing several setbacks.

373
00:29:32,839 --> 00:29:33,960
I've personally experienced it.

374
00:29:34,680 --> 00:29:37,079
So I won't get scared off by these hardships in front of us.

375
00:29:37,319 --> 00:29:38,920
Recently,

376
00:29:39,599 --> 00:29:41,279
I was also demotivated.

377
00:29:41,279 --> 00:29:42,480
But...

378
00:29:42,480 --> 00:29:44,559
I have an emotional attachment to Zhirong.

379
00:29:45,039 --> 00:29:47,160
So I decided to stay.

380
00:29:47,599 --> 00:29:49,200
I'll work hard with all of you...

381
00:29:49,319 --> 00:29:50,960
to restore our company's grandeur.

382
00:29:52,319 --> 00:29:53,960
To be honest, Mr. Hou Junior,

383
00:29:54,160 --> 00:29:56,480
I actually hesitated for a long time...

384
00:29:56,640 --> 00:29:58,000
before deciding to stay.

385
00:29:58,680 --> 00:30:01,759
I'm in charge of the company's day-to-day operations.

386
00:30:01,920 --> 00:30:03,200
I'm worried that if I leave,

387
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:04,519
you won't be able to handle it alone.

388
00:30:04,519 --> 00:30:06,039
That's why I decided to stay.

389
00:30:06,240 --> 00:30:07,880
But let me make myself clear.

390
00:30:07,880 --> 00:30:09,400
I'm only helping you out for the time being...

391
00:30:09,400 --> 00:30:10,599
