395
00:30:15,119 --> 00:30:16,200
It's okay.

396
00:30:16,200 --> 00:30:18,799
The company is allowing everyone to come and go as they wish now.

397
00:30:20,359 --> 00:30:21,920
I'm planning...

398
00:30:22,359 --> 00:30:23,920
