405
00:30:37,640 --> 00:30:40,359
That way, we can all be closer.

406
00:30:40,359 --> 00:30:43,119
Secondly, I can lessen some of the company's burden.

407
00:30:43,799 --> 00:30:46,319
Mr. Hou Junior, I support your idea.

